OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry through
OL,6,Fthe evening and overnight. Clear skies
OL,7,Fseeing the development of some low
OL,8,Fcloud, mist and fog by dawn. Light
OL,9,Fwinds but breezy along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FEarly low cloud, mist and
OL,12,Ffog clearing to leave a dry, bright
OL,13,Fand mild afternoon. Cloud thickening
OL,14,Finto the evening however, bringing a
OL,15,Fthreat of rain to end the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
